data.description: Lake Home Fixer Upper with stunning views! This property has much to offer with the spacious yard, and the short distance to the beach area with playground equipment, picnic tables and shower house.  The home features lots of living space with 1,232 Sq. Ft. on each level, many windows and entry ways, attached garage, large main bedroom, walk in closets, and open living space.
